<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When rendering the input field with Zend_View_Helper_FormFile, it will output the current value of the form element, which is the current uploaded file including absolute path. This is not supported by browsers anyway and is a security issue, so the output of the value in the tag should be removed.</p>

